Data Attribution:
The dataset used in this project (Eurostat NRG_IND_REN) is published by
Eurostat, the Statistical Office of the European Union, and is free for reuse
with attribution under Eurostat's standard reuse policy.
Source: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/product/view/NRG_IND_REN

Map Data Attribution:
The geographic boundaries are from Natural Earth / World Atlas TopoJSON,
released to the public domain.
Source: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/world-atlas@2/countries-110m.json
